<item>
            <title>[LU-3349] Add b2_3/b2_4 ldisk image tarball for conf-sanity.sh test_32</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3349</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Create a filesystem image with Lustre 2.3.0 for use by conf-sanity.sh test_32() in later releases of Lustre.  This allows testing that the newer releases of Lustre can upgrade a filesystem that was previously formatted and used at the earlier version.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="19031">LU-3349</key>
            <summary>Add b2_3/b2_4 ldisk image tarball for conf-sanity.sh test_32</summary>
